snippet.title: Slenderman Must Die: Chapter7 - Abandoned Graveyard
snippet.description:
Android Download - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PoisonGames.SMDC7AbandonedGraveyard
PC Download - https://gamejolt.com/games/SlendermanMustDieChapter7AbandonedGraveyard/292774

New Slenderman Must Die Chapter + Halloween Special

This time you are at the Abandoned Graveyard. Your mission is simple, 
huntdown and kill Slenderman.
His Body is hidden inside the Creepy Church. Find it and BURN it.

In Halloween Special - Explore the big city and find 9 green pumpkins.

*** Features ***

- Three weapons: Pistol, Shotgun and AK74M
- Smooth Controls
- High quality 3D environment graphics
- Gameplay from Poison Games that you love.
- Explore The Abandoned Graveyard, Catacombs and Old Church!
